WASH Survey Indicators Data for Dhaka, Bangladesh

Source: R/data.R
indicatorsDataBGD.Rd

WASH survey indicators data calculated from survey raw data

indicatorsDataBGD

Format

A data frame with 162 variables and 1282 entries
